OL,7,FMozdah hasn't seen her parents or
OL,8,Fsiblings for three years - and said it
OL,9,Fis difficult to stay hopeful
OL,11,FA long awaited reunion route has
OL,12,Fopened for Afghan families separated
OL,13,Fduring the evacuation of Kabul, nearly
OL,14,Fthree years since the Taliban takeover.
OL,16,FIn the chaos of the withdrawal of
OL,17,FWestern Forces from Afghanistan in
OL,18,FAugust 2021, thousands of people were
OL,19,Fseparated and family members left
OL,20,Fbehind.
