OL,7,FNow those who were able to escape to
OL,8,Fthe UK can apply for their partners
OL,9,Fand family to join them.
OL,11,F"There remains an urgent need to
OL,12,Fensure that those who assisted our
OL,13,Fefforts in Afghanistan, often at huge
OL,14,Fpersonal risk to themselves and their
OL,15,Ffamilies, can be reunited,"
OL,16,FImmigration and Citizenship Minister
OL,17,FSeema Malhotra said.
