OL,7,FWhen the evacuation from Kabul
OL,8,Fstarted, Muhammad's daughter was just
OL,9,Fa few months old and his son was aged
OL,10,F18 months.
OL,12,FThe family decided the risk at the
OL,13,Fairport was too great, and while he
OL,14,Fwas airlifted to the UK, his wife and
OL,15,Fchildren fled across the border to
OL,16,FPakistan.
