OL,7,FAs the years have passed, hopes of a
OL,8,Fspeedy reunion in the UK have faded.
OL,9,FMuhammed told ITV News that the family
OL,10,Fhas now gone into in hiding in
OL,11,FPakistan with the threat of
OL,12,Fdeportation back to Taliban ruled
OL,13,FAfghanistan hanging over them.
OL,15,FDuring his daily video calls,
OL,16,FMuhammed's wife told us of the mental
OL,17,Ftoll this prolonged separation is
OL,18,Fhaving on her.
