OL,7,F"Alone with two children, it's very
OL,8,Fhard for me to be in a strange country
OL,9,Fwithout my husband. They (the British
OL,10,Fgovernment) should please help us,"
OL,11,Fshe pleaded.
OL,13,FAs a civil engineer, Muhammed worked
OL,14,Falongside British forces but now feels
OL,15,Fbetrayed.
OL,17,FHe's been moved between several
OL,18,Fdifferent Home Office run hotels in
OL,19,Fthe south of England for nearly three
OL,20,Fyears, a situation that has left him
OL,21,Ffeeling suicidal.
