OL,7,F"All I ask for is a regular life with
OL,8,Fmy parents, with my family."
OL,10,FMozdah was 19 when she was airlifted
OL,11,Fto safety, part of a group of female
OL,12,FAfghan footballers who had fled for
OL,13,Ftheir lives and escaped the Taliban
OL,14,Fvia Pakistan.
OL,16,FIt's three years since she last saw
OL,17,Fher parents and siblings who remain
OL,18,Ftrapped in Afghanistan. Mozdah has
OL,19,Ftried to build a new life in South
OL,20,FYorkshire but told me of the heartache
OL,21,Fshe feels so deeply every day.
