OL,7,FSevin is still separated from her
OL,8,Fwider family after fleeing Afghanistan
OL,9,Fthree years ago.
OL,11,FUnder the Taliban, women's rights have
OL,12,Fbeen crushed. Sevin was among 130
OL,13,Fyoung female footballers and their
OL,14,Ffamilies who escaped.
OL,16,FIt took four months, but an
OL,17,Finternational rescue effort involving
OL,18,FLeeds United and some funding from
OL,19,Freality TV star Kim Kardashian
OL,20,Feventually brought them to the UK.
