OL,7,FAs a woman in Afghanistan, playing
OL,8,Ffootball put their lives at risk, but
OL,9,Fit was also their means of escape.
OL,11,FWhen Sevin talks about the game her
OL,12,Fwhole face lights up. "It is my life,
OL,13,Fmy love," she tells me.
OL,15,FThe 23-year-old travelled to the UK
OL,16,Fwith her mother and younger siblings
OL,17,Fbut still feels the pain of being
OL,18,Fseparated from her wider family.
