OL,7,F"Every night when I want to sleep I am
OL,8,Fjust think of my dad and sisters and
OL,9,Fall the girls in Afghanistan. They
OL,10,Fdon't have freedom, they can't do
OL,11,Fanything", she said.
OL,13,FThe family has tried to start a new
OL,14,Flife in Doncaster where Sevin has
OL,15,Fenrolled in a sports science course
OL,16,Fand her mother Faqia, 45, runs a fish
OL,17,Fand chip shop in the town.
OL,19,FBut three years of separation from her
OL,20,Fhusband has taken its toll.
