OL,8,FPlease don't let people like me suffer
OL,9,Fanymore from this separation," Faqia
OL,10,Ftold ITV News.
OL,12,F"Please do something to help us. It is
OL,13,Fnot good to lose your hope, but I feel
OL,14,Fthere is no hope."
