OL,7,FWhat do the statistics show?
OL,9,FThe latest official figures showed
OL,10,Fthat almost as many Afghan nationals
OL,11,Farrived in the UK having made the
OL,12,FChannel crossing as through the
OL,13,FGovernment's legal routes last year.
OL,15,FAfghans are the top nationality
OL,16,Farriving by small boats, making up
OL,17,Falmost a fifth of all Channel arrivals.
OL,19,FNearly 6000 made the dangerous
OL,20,Fcrossing in the year ending March 2024.
