OL,7,FWhat is the Afghan Citizens
OL,8,FResettlement Scheme (ACRS) separated
OL,9,Ffamilies route?
OL,11,FThe ACRS opened on Tuesday July 30th,
OL,12,Fand the Government said the window to
OL,13,Fsubmit an expression of interest will
OL,14,Fremain open for three months, until
OL,15,FOctober 30.
OL,17,FThe scheme formally opened in January
OL,18,F2022, with the then government
OL,19,Fpledging to resettle up to 20,000
OL,20,Fpeople "over the coming years".
